data.description: Beautifully Rehabbed Cape Cod offers all new kitchen with white shaker cabinets, quartz counters and island, a cooks dream generous prep space. The kitchen overlooks the dining room and deck for grilling out. Gleaming hardwoods floors throughout. First floor primary bedroom, two bedrooms upstairs and additional one is in the finished basement. The finished basement also includes a family room, bar and mini wet sink area. You'll also find a real laundry room with extra space to fold and storage. All new fixtures throughout, fresh paint, new floors, 200 amp service, everything for today's busy lifestyle. Ready to just move in and enjoy.  Driveway that leads to a 2.5 car garage, spacious yard with storage shed. Seller will credit 3K for appliances so you can make this your own.
